<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Taft College participates in the Advanced Placement Program and will accept scores of 3, 4, or 5 on AP Exams for elective credit. The student will receive a grade of credit (CR).</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.taftcollege.edu/student_services/pdf/Catalog2010-2012.pdf" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
